review_blob:
This is my favorite dark beer. Although it does not taste very dark, it brings a rich, full flavor of dark beer that is not too harsh. It has a fine look and long-lasting distinguished taste.

Everything from this brewery is a hit. If you want to try a lighter brew, try their La Fin Du Monde.

Great, clean beer with a good texture for such a light ale. Too bad my distributor has discontinued it...
Enjoi!
